A '''directional landing beacon''', also known as a '''directional guidance beacon'''<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> and an '''automated beacon''',<ref name="DIRP">{{DarkStryder|adventure=Death Is Remotely Possible|book=The DarkStryder Campaign}}</ref> was a device that transmitted fixed signals that [[Starship/Legends|starships]] used to orient themselves in [[Realspace/Legends|space]].

[[Drone barge/Legends|Drone barges]] were equipped with [[Beacon Sensor|sensors]] that allowed them to home in on the beacons while in [[Spaceport/Legends|port]].<ref name="EGTD" />

